<Base
  title="Houzz Pro vs Contractor Foreman 2026 — Which Is Right for Small Contractors?"
  description="Houzz Pro vs Contractor Foreman: polished residential software vs. budget-friendly all-in-one. Honest comparison for small contractors choosing between them."
